{"tid":1033264,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"男校我只服皇仁","createTime":"2019-02-23T04:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:18:59.000Z","uid":198730,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f045c40e6d6cbc4252152284ab8fc6c04cdf9a79","tid":1033264,"uid":198730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:01:34.000Z","msg":"公屋仔，默默耕耘，薯足成世，最終內涵致勝，只不過忍辱一時，卻成為人生赢家。唔似果啲自細身嬌肉貴嘅公子哥，中學讀要入股嘅貴族學校，每年四十萬up培養國際視野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，每個月洗幾萬蚊請外國人教琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要請埋營養師添，或者果啲所謂名男校，日日hit plane話自己有幾耐歷史，但出到黎入大學率極低，校友又唔夠皇仁勁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吾皇萬歲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3b1b871b0b8d2f9775a8a8cef63510f1144728","tid":1033264,"uid":152508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"知你讀皇仁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5ba1cb92b9449493a36d713d90dc0b42bfe2e7","tid":1033264,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"都唔係全部都係公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9f5e2f26f240970e8f0edf0d1777ac1469452f","tid":1033264,"uid":4526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"人地去外國浸鹹水日日屌鬼妹 畢業就入daddy間公司做野<br />\n<br />\n班公屋仔HKU 1st hon咪又要幫人執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe4d74711ca39cd1972464a191e25e7c828dbc3","tid":1033264,"uid":198730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"